>6 月 30 日星期日：</strong>上午晚些时候多云转晴，最高气温 20°C，最低气温 10°C</p><p><em>最后更新时间：6 月 29 日上午 8 点 30 分</em></p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-jayahadadream-emerging-talent-competition-winner-interview-radar-3751748">认识 JayaHadADream——2024 年格拉斯顿伯里新兴人才大赛的获胜者</a></strong></li></ul><div class="gel-body-copy gs-u-mb++" lang="en"><div><figure id="attachment_3256526" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3256526" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3256526" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/GLASTO_JACKWHITE_PARK_SUNDAY_EVAPENTEL_3119.jpg" alt="观看 Jack White 2022 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节秘密演出的人群" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/GLASTO_JACKWHITE_PARK_SUNDAY_EVAPENTEL_3119.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/GLASTO_JACKWHITE_PARK_SUNDAY_EVAPENTEL_3119-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/GLASTO_JACKWHITE_PARK_SUNDAY_EVAPENTEL_3119-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/GLASTO_JACKWHITE_PARK_SUNDAY_EVAPENTEL_3119-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/GLASTO_JACKWHITE_PARK_SUNDAY_EVAPENTEL_3119-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/GLASTO_JACKWHITE_PARK_SUNDAY_EVAPENTEL_3119-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3256526" class="wp-caption-text"> 2022 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 (Glastonbury) 公园里，观众聚集在一起观看 Jack White 的秘密演出。图片来源：Eva Pentel for NME</figcaption></figure></div><div><p>去年，由于气温达到 20 多度，而且现场基本上保持干燥和阳光明媚，音乐节组织者发布了在高温下保持安全的建议。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/photos/glastonbury-2016-things-have-got-even-muddier-down-on-worthy-farm-1407268">Glasto 观众上一次经历大雨和泥泞是在 2016 年</a>，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/coldplay-end-glastonbury-2016-with-the-most-batshit-crazy-pyramid-stage-set-ever-6307">酷玩乐队 (Coldplay) 名列前茅</a>。</p><p>其他消息方